# Agent Rules

## Core Instructions
- Always refer to [PRD.md](file:///Users/machos/.gemini/antigravity/brain/a56948ae-b292-49c5-a870-c402e2f67b29/PRD.md) and [guidelines.md](file:///Users/machos/Blog/jekyll-blog/guidelines.md) before making changes.
- Comment all non-obvious Jekyll logic or Liquid templates.
- If a requested feature requires a new plugin, verify compatibility with GitHub Pages first.
- Maintain simple and scalable code over clever abstractions.

## File Handling
- Do not delete `_config.yml` or `Gemfile`.
- When creating new posts, prompt for a title and date if not provided.
